g.com/50/v2-6a37605aaf9e4247c9f0e45343adca15_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1729040137.638640","card_id":"Q_887741740","target":{"id":887741740,"title":"如何看待 9 月出口总值 2.1653 万亿，增速仅为 1.6%？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/887741740","type":"question","created":1728897093,"answer_count":44,"follower_count":157,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[472,3714,5273,12230,20242],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"海关总署新闻发言人、统计分析司司长吕大良介绍，9月当月，我国出口2.17万亿元，增长了1.6%，增速确实有所放缓，初步分析，主要是受一些短期偶发因素的影响。首先，跟9月份的极端天气有一定的关系，9月两次台风接连在长三角地区登陆，历史数据也显示，台风对出口的影响持续时间比较长，台风过后船队的排期往往会顺延，出口有所滞后。其次，前段时间受全球航运不畅、集装箱短缺，以及美国东海岸码头工人合同到期谈判预期等的影响，企业的出货、物流节奏有所调整，数据也显示，部分产品往年出口旺季是在三季度，今年提前了一个多月。此外，去年9月出口规模基数是比较高的，是年内的次高，仅次于12月份，基数偏高也制约了今年9月的同比增速。总的来说，9月当月出口增速的放缓属于短期内正常的数据波动。 海关总署：9月我国出口2.17万亿元，增长1.6% _ 东方财富网"},"attached_info":"CkAI/4es9qrh77N+EAMaCTExMTE0NTkyOCDFwLO4BjAAOJ0BQBZyCTg4Nzc0MTc0MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"5.8 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-3a6f5c141fd271e8e9ba2a6beadb79dc_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1729040137.639574","card_id":"Q_26570985","target":{"id":26570985,"title":"有没有一本讲解gpu和CUDA编程的经典入门书籍？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/26570985","type":"question","created":1415693666,"answer_count":63,"follower_count":3149,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[870,1771,6901,9995,15681],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj0I/4es9qrh77N+EAMaBzI4MTEzMzAg4oqHowUwADjNGEAXcggyNjU3MDk4NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"5.8 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c